// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0354 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: aa51d1a2-32a9-5990-ad1a-cf5d8de50db5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*")
